Name:           kf6-kitemmodels
Version:        6.12.0
Release:        0
Summary:        Set of item models extending the Qt model-view framework
License:        LGPL-2.1-or-later
URL:            https://www.kde.org
Source:         %{rname}-%{version}.tar.xz
